Like, if you walk past, you’re walking down the college,
Everything’s so dull and you see this

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:46.480
it’s the first thing you’d wanna come over and be like
“Oh, what’s this? What’s that?”

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:50.640
